CeloPG invites builders, developers, and community members to contribute to the Celo ecosystem. Interested parties can:Apply for Funding: Submit proposals through the Celo Public Goods Hub (celopg.eco) for grants, incubation, or RPGF programs.

Vote on Proposals: Celo holders can participate in governance through the Celo Public Goods Snapshot space.

Join the Community: Register interest via forms on celopg.eco or email stewards@celopg.eco to collaborate on initiatives.

